fields.name: Felt Squeegee and 9MM Retractable Blade
fields.description:
Get our Combo Deal which includes a 9mm retractable steel blade and a Felt Edge Plastic Squeegee.

The Squeegee is made from flexible plastic and is an essential application tool to ensure you achieve a professional finish when installing any vinyl, decal, tape or film. It allows conforming to curves and recesses while still applying strong pressure.

It can be used for fitting all types of digital printed vinyls, cut vinyls,wrapping vinyls, window graphics etc.

Squeegee Size: 100mm x 75mm 

- Essential tool to achieve bubble free application
- Unlike rigid plastic applicators this flexible tool can be used to work vinyl into curves and recesses
- Tough and durable so they can be used again and again

fields.name: Felt Edge Squeegee
fields.description:
Our Felt Edge squeegee is made from flexible plastic and is an essential application tool to ensure you achieve a professional finish when installing any vinyl, decal, tape or film. It allows conforming to curves and recesses while still applying strong pressure.

The felt edge makes it perfect for applying soft or textured material without risking scratches and it can be used for fitting all types of digital printed vinyls, cut vinyls,wrapping vinyls, window graphics etc.

Size: 100mm x 75mm 

- Essential tool to achieve bubble free application
- Unlike rigid plastic applicators this flexible tool can be used to work vinyl into curves and recesses
- Tough and durable so they can be used again and again

fields.name: Cotton Application Gloves
fields.description:
A Pair of Cotton Gloves, ideal for vehicle wrapping.

Size: Medium

fields.name: 9MM Cutting Knife with Retractable Blade
fields.description:
9mm Cutting Knife features a steel body with stainless steel blade and slit tail piece for snapping off blunt blades.

We also sell a 50pk of 9mm Stainless steel blades here.

fields.name: 9MM Cutting Blades - 50 Pieces
fields.description:
Pack of 50 x 9mm Knife Blades for use with our 9mm Knife. Also can be used in any Olfa SVR1/2, XA-1 knives.

It can be used for cutting all types of digital printed vinyls,wrapping vinyls, window Tinting and graphics etc.

- Designed not to scratch Glass
- 13 snap off points per blade

fields.name: Conquerer Squeegee
fields.description:
The Conquerer comes with a 17cm rubber edge which is molded to the body (not glued) and will not peel away. A true must have for any serious tinter.

Size: 17 x 8cm (6.5 x 3 inch)

fields.name: 5%(Limo Black) Eco Film
fields.description:
This 5% Window Tint Film is a non-reflective film with classic looks, it offers cutting-edge technological improvements for clarity and ease of use. It is the darkest tint we offer and is also commonly known as Limo Black. 
 
The Width of the Window Tint Rolls are 152cm (60inch). It can be applied to Automotive and Architectural Glass. 
 
Brand - Chromatic Vinyl Films
Light Transmission - 5%
IR - 60%
U/V Rejected - 99%
Size - 1.52 X 5 Meters
This is sufficient to tint a 4 door car including the rear glass.
 
We also have a large range of Window Tinting tools.

fields.name: 5%(Limo Black) Carbon Film
fields.description:
This 5% Window Tint Film is a non-reflective film with Nano technology film containing carbon particles that boasts great heat rejection and colour stability for a lifetime. It is the darkest tint we offer and is also commonly known as Limo Black.

The Width of the Window Tint Rolls are 152cm (60inch). It can be applied to Automotive and Architectural Glass.

Construction: Carbon Coating Polyester Film
Colour: Standard Black
Layer: 2-ply
Thickness: 1.5 mil
Scratch Resistant: Yes
Reflective: No
Metal: No
Ultra Violet Block: 99%
Visible Light Transmission: 5%
TSER Rejected: 28-58%
Size - 1.52 X 5 Meters
This is sufficient to tint a 4 door car including the rear glass.

We also have a large range of Window Tinting tools.

fields.name: 5%(Limo Black) Premium Ceramic Film
fields.description:
This 5% Window Tint Film is a Ceramic film is the highest quality of window tint film and also one of the most expensive. Our film contains neither metal, dye, nor carbon. Composed of nanoceramic particles that are nonconductive and non-metallic.

The Width of the Window Tint Rolls are 152cm (60inch). It can be applied to Automotive and Architectural Glass.

SUPERIOR SOLAR PROTECTION: 99% IRR rejection (heat), 99% UV rejection (radiation), 63% TSER (total solar energy rejected), 70% glare reduction

Visible Light Transmission: 5%
Size - 1.52 X 5 Meters
This is sufficient to tint a 4 door car including the rear glass.

We also have a large range of Window Tinting tools.
